<figureCitation id="F1507DB0E241F0AB04019A1B24072E4F" captionStart="Figure 10" captionStartId="F10" captionText="Figure 10. Pristepyris tainanensis, male, paratype A head in full-face view B mandible C mesosoma in lateral view (mirror-reversed); arrow indicating an angulate corner present on cervical pronotal area D mesosoma in dorsal view; arrow indicating transverse pronotal carinae present. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1102.84953.figure10" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/686038" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Fig. 10</figureCitation>
